# Project Conventions

## Stack
- Framework: Next.js (App Router)
- Language: TypeScript
- Styling: Tailwind CSS
- Package manager: npm

## Conventions
- Components: functional, PascalCase filenames
- Commits: Conventional Commits format (feat:, fix:, chore:, docs:)
- Prefer named exports over default exports

## Notes for AI assistant
- This is a frontend-focused capstone project for an AI-assisted development track.
- Explain reasoning when making architectural suggestions.